1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 20]

14
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,390
[Goodness And Virtue Bring Fragrance]
First bow to the heaven and earth.

15
00:00:48,150 --> 00:00:50,280
Second bow to your parents,

16
00:00:51,110 --> 00:00:53,640
Then bow to each other.

17
00:01:30,310 --> 00:01:32,480
Our destinies don't align,

18
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:38,900
♪Playing the Guqin under the moon,
recalling his poem♪

19
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,040
our hearts diverge,

20
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:54,510
and our paths diverge.

21
00:01:54,540 --> 00:01:57,660
♪Years have passed, the flowers
have bloomed again♪

22
00:01:57,980 --> 00:02:01,540
♪In this life without you,
day and night feel endless♪

23
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:05,060
♪In this old dreamland,
memories of past lives are locked away♪

24
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:08,380
♪I didn't see you when I woke up
and opened the windows♪

25
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:10,560
Thus,

26
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,630
let's part ways amicably,

27
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:18,400
each finding our own happiness.

28
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:23,180
[Divorce Letter]

29
00:02:23,220 --> 00:02:26,740
♪We didn't know
or understand each other♪

30
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:31,060
♪Unbothered by worldly affairs♪

31
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:37,980
♪All perils stop on my brow
as I await your return♪

32
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,800
Sister,

33
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,560
oh, I should say,

34
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:50,710
little sister.

35
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:53,310
As the wife, I haven't even
taken my seat,

36
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,750
yet you, a concubine,
have already started dining.

37
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,280
Isn't that against the rules?

38
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:01,800
What kind of attitude is this?

39
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:03,590
How dare you, a mere concubine,

40
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,470
not respond to the wife's questions?

41
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,560
This is for not following the rules!

42
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,240
You...

43
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,360
Maids!

44
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:32,030
Teach this wretched woman a lesson!

45
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,150
What's going on?

46
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,310
Ling,

47
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:51,400
I merely lectured Wan'er a little.

48
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,360
And she resorted to violence.

49
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,520
My face is not disfigured, is it?

50
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,800
Hanfeng,

51
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:00,710
take her back to her room.

52
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,120
Yes, My Lord.

53
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:14,520
Ling,

54
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,600
my face hurts.

55
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:27,820
♪I spread out paper and pen,
writing a quatrain♪

56
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:35,020
♪I think of you again
as I write down the past memories♪

57
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:41,020
♪Who did I share my emotions with
during those years?♪

58
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:44,750
Ling, for the past ten years,

59
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,750
I've been fantasizing
about marrying you.

60
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,480
Now,

61
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,920
the dream has finally come true.

62
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,870
Why don't you stay tonight?

63
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,480
You know

64
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:58,390
why I went along with your act.

65
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,920
Dreams really are easily shattered.

66
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,000
Sometimes I really wonder

67
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,720
what it is about Su Wan'er
that you like.

68
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,160
Does one need a reason to like someone?

69
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,430
Just like I like you
for your martial prowess,

70
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,190
extraordinary demeanor,

71
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,920
and unparalleled greatness.

72
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,160
I could go on listing reasons
for three days and nights.

73
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:19,920
But my love for her

74
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,430
doesn't require any reason.

75
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,600
You see,

76
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,750
even your ruthlessness

77
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,160
is enough to captivate me.

78
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,360
I never expected you

79
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,390
to like me this much.

80
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,870
Of course.

81
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:41,240
One of us is madly in love,

82
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,190
and the other one
is obsessively infatuated.

83
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,390
It's only right for us to be together.

84
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:47,000
Ling...

85
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,830
What's wrong?

86
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,240
Are you all right?

87
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,160
It's the cold syndrome.

88
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:01,310
I've been tormented
by it for many years.

89
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,560
You know that better than anyone.

90
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,630
I could die at any moment.

91
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,240
But it's not a full moon today.

92
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,510
Why would it attack early?

93
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,310
I'm hungry.

94
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,510
Go ask the kitchen
to prepare food for me.

95
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,510
I...

96
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:20,510
What's the matter?

97
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,390
Are you starving me
because I'm a concubine?

98
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,040
I won't dare to.

99
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,240
Are you trying to trick me
into giving you the antidote?

100
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,800
What do you take me for?

101
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,040
That's Wan'er's lifesaving medicine.

102
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,310
I'd rather die than take it.

103
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,950
Even if you want to die,
I won't let you.

104
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,510
You really are tricking me.

105
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,270
My Lord.

106
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,270
Take her away.

107
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,000
The effects of this Cold Powder

108
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,360
really resemble the cold symptoms.

109
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:30,680
My Lord,

110
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:33,190
this is the only antidote
that can treat your cold symptoms.

111
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,510
If you give it to Her Ladyship,

112
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,870
your life will be in danger.

113
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,600
Nothing is more important than her life.

114
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,430
Wan'er?

115
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:06,380
[To Ling Xiao]

116
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:17,500
[Divorce Letter]

117
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:39,740
♪People sit silently
by candlelight as night begins♪

118
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:45,620
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

119
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:50,900
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

120
00:08:51,020 --> 00:08:52,580
♪Everyone is filled
with sorrow and pity♪

121
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:56,460
♪Alas, the mortal world
has too many spectators♪

122
00:08:57,980 --> 00:09:03,580
♪You turn back to ascend
the stage wearing a green robe♪

123
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:09,340
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

124
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:15,140
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

125
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,620
♪You sing for me♪

126
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:20,540
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

127
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:26,580
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

128
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:32,740
♪The heart is closed,
unable to gaze at the emotional eyes♪

129
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:35,700
♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

130
00:09:35,860 --> 00:09:39,380
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪

131
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:42,860
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪